c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eSocial Justice \\u0026#x26; Civil Rights\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe stand for equality and justice for all people regardless of race, gender, sexual orientation, gender identity, religion, or national origin. We oppose discrimination in all its forms and support criminal justice reform, voting rights, and immigration reform that treats all people with dignity.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eDemocracy \\u0026#x26; Good Government\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe believe in transparent, accountable government that serves the people. We support campaign finance reform, voting rights protections, and ending gerrymandering. We oppose voter suppression and fight to ensure every eligible citizen can exercise their right to vote.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eRural Communities\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eAs a rural county, we understand the unique challenges facing our communities. We support expanding broadband access, investing in rural healthcare, protecting family farms and ranches, and ensuring that rural voices are heard in Sacramento and Washington.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eGun Safety\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe support common-sense gun safety measures that protect our communities while respecting responsible gun ownership. We believe we can reduce gun violence through universal background checks, red flag laws, and research into gun violence prevention.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"10:[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative overflow-hidden bg-dem-blue py-16 sm:py-20\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"absolute inset-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L18\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"/images/hero-vote.jpg\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Democracy and civic engagement\\\",\\\"fill\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"object-cover opacity-20\\\",\\\"priority\\\":true}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\